    "name": {
      "zh": "马林 MXLR .308 ME 杠杆步枪",
      "en": "Marlin MXLR .308 ME lever-action rifle"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "MXLR",
      "en": "MXLR"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "经典的马林 1895 型杠杆步枪，MXLR (.308 ME 杠杆革命) 版本。这款步枪以现代技术重新诠释了亨利式杠杆式步枪的经典设计，枪身部件采用镀铬表面处理，发射独特的 .308 Marlin Express 步枪弹。",
      "en": "The classic Marlin 1895 lever-action rifle in the MXLR (Marlin Express LEVERevolution) variant. A modern take on the timeless Henry-style lever-action. Comes in a chrome finish and chambered for the special .308 Marlin Express cartridge."
    },
